commit.message:
plugin: Put custom CLI options in "tornado" group

Previously, the command-line options were added to the default group, labelled
"custom options" by Pytest. This commit puts the options in a group labelled
"tornado options", separating them from other options in order to make it clear
where they come from. This is especially useful in environments where multiple
plugins are used.

commit.message:
Make create_cert platform independent

NamedTemporaryFiles cannot be reopen while still open on Windows. By closing it first, we can use it. So we have to manage deletion manually.
Release 0.7.0
Make it possible to use base_url with https and without.
